attributes.title: Trump stole my thingsğŸ˜
attributes.review: I used to like Donald Trump but after I downloaded this app he sent someone to my house to take away my cat, dog,car, house and phone. The people who took my belonging were secret services and I asked could I have them back but they said they were selling it because he needed the money for his campaign. You lost my vote for the election, Biden2020.
